      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NICKO QUEEN (2) was checked in the run and safely held when fifth (21.35) in a Grade 5 over 365m at this track. Should be in this for a long way. NICKO KING (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 21.29 beating Natural Essence. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should be in this for a long way. GOODBYE MATE (7) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (20.12) behind Lucky Winner at Goulburn. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Will give a great sight again. WAR HAWK (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
